{"tid":1409132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18區街坊同我聽住！","createTime":"2019-08-04T19:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T20:05:13.000Z","uid":204200,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8da7d9e8c5055d610473a10b2aa1d82e452a3e3","tid":1409132,"uid":204200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:25:54.000Z","msg":"經過呢幾個星期以嚟，各區街坊已經漸漸成為了每區最後防線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人真係進步得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前線唔再係孤軍作戰<br />\n<br />\n今日各區街坊玩完之後真係做到be water，全部都好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽朝係和理非主場，除左各個集會之外<br />\n希望大家可以做到零消費，罷工罷市，唔好比啲冇罷工嘅舖賺到盡！<br />\n<br />\n另外，我呼籲各位街坊可以記錄一下 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇罷工</span> 嘅店舖，喺過左8月5之後發起新嘅清算行動<br />\n<br />\n罷買又好，接放工又好，永不篤灰，永不割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"fbc84d841aca309de040753a071dee83eeb1eb8a","tid":1409132,"uid":204200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:36:13.000Z","msg":"發夢發得多，個人暈陀陀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫我停狗鐵，唔係就好易跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7點半見</span>"},{"pid":"06c70a729b85770fab1544903d5a22ba7d73793b","tid":1409132,"uid":204200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:52:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814cc7452a6a9ed2ac03bc7c370d22ae5c21dbda","tid":1409132,"uid":204200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:52:14.000Z","msg":"再自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412cab67899a0016d7a2bfcfe7bdf9a792b2f621","tid":1409132,"uid":204200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"